THE COMING OF THE SAUCERS
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    70 years ago, at 3.00pm on the 24th June 1947 Kenneth Arnold, an
    experienced Search and Rescue pilot was flying over the Cascade
    Mountains in Washington State in America when he saw below him nine
    unusual objects travelling at a speed he estimated to be around
    1200 miles per hour. His immediate reaction was they were snow
    geese but having considered their speed he thought that they may be
    jet planes...

