OVER 2000 POUNDS RAISED AT CHARITY ART AUCTION
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    On Friday 9th June, Richmond upon Thames College (RuTC) was the
    venue for a special charity auction featuring the hidden work of
    the late artist, Desmond Jones. The auction, which was hosted by
    BBC Auctioneer Charlie Ross, raised 2575 pounds and benefitted
    over 30 charities with a local or personal connection to the
    artist.

